    <h2>Collaboration</h2>
<p class="con">Starting in academic year 2014,  Ganpat  University (GNU), and IBM (under its Career Education program) have agreed to 
    launch Engineering programs with specialization using IBM Software. 
    The aim is to develop sufficient industry needed skills for manpower on critical emerging technology area such as Cloud,
    Mobility, Big Data & Analytics.</p>

<p class="con">IBM - Career Education program is a holistic, comprehensive one with customized offerings for Engineering and 
    Business Schools, students and faculty members. The programs bring together the latest software content, real-world 
    industry experiences, hands-on lab courses, current practices and case studies for the participants to have engaged learning.</p>
<p class=" con">IBM and GNU have collaborated to setup an IBM Software Lab for Emerging Technologies in the campus to help students
    and faculty members enhance their skills in areas of Big Data & Analytics, Cloud Computing, and Mobility. 
    The industry collaborated courses in association with IBM provide a unique platform to the students to 
    have hands-on experience with live projects, which are mentored by industry experts.
    This enables students to attain industry-readiness and transform themselves into highly employable trained professionals.</p>

<p>Key Features </p> 
<ul>
<li>Relevant theoretical and practical knowledge.</li>

<li>Curriculum designed and delivered by a mix of qualified  and experienced instructors from Ganpat University, IBM and from industry.</li>


<li>Hands on sessions at IBM Software Lab for Emerging Technologies on campus equipped with current tools and software.</li>


<li>Campus having a state-of-the-art infrastructure and convenient accessibility from Ahmedabad and Gandhinagar.</li>

<li>Online resource management through learning management system (LMS).</li>

<li>Access to IBM’s Learning Resources; online and in printed form.</li>

<li>Real world projects and experiential learning.</li>

<li>Regular Industry Visit and Interaction with Industry Practitioners.</li>

<li>Extra Curricular Activities for holistic development.</li>

<li>Preparing students for competitive exams, recruitment tests, and entrance examinations like  GPSC / CAT / GRE + GATE etc.
    as an  audit course.</li>
    </ul>


<p>Program Advantages</p>

<p class="con">Join a technically sophisticated workforce as successful, practicing engineers in a wide range of software engineering fields.

Relevant theoretical and practical knowledge to understand Cloud Computing and highlight key capabilities of Cloud Based Applications. 

Understand core technical concepts related to Applications Development on Cloud (Platform as a Service), Mobile Applications and highlight key capabilities of Enterprise Mobility, Business Intelligence, Big Data Analytics along with Hadoop Architecture.

Aligning Technology to the need of Business.

Fundamental Software Engineering Concepts like Software Development Life Cycle , Application Development , Database Management System and many more.

Use cutting edge Analytical Tools to Find , Interpret , Analyze Business Data.

Pursue advanced degrees in engineering, business, or other professional fields.</p>
